  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1702942">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1702942/" class="title-link">当代女性现状浅析</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1702942"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/JoyYoung/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1630639-5.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/JoyYoung/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">飞天PP猪</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-02-19"
      class="main-meta">2009-02-19 02:59:46</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1702942_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  从波伏娃之后的半个多世纪的情况来看，并不是完全如波伏娃所预料的，女性会越来越取得平等的权利和尊重的地位。相反，世界女权运动和世界无产阶级运动一样，充满了迂回与曲折，并缓慢上升，成陀螺波浪形。   1904年日俄战争爆发，俄国妇女涌上街头，进行游行示威；1939年到1945...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1702942/#comments">(104回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">378有用 / 11没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1702942_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1702942_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5200449">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5200449/" class="title-link">你与我相似：《第二性》与性别平等</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5200449"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/3347336/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3347336-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3347336/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">dormouse</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-12-05"
      class="main-meta">2011-12-05 17:31:50</span>
</div>

